divs: Sighting DetailsI was at Bradford Beach on the Coast of Lake Michigan between 9-11 PM. Me and my Friends noticed a group of airplane-like objects moving in a row slowly through the sky. They were close enough to us that if they were airplanes, we would of heard a loud sound. Also, they were moving far too slow to be airplanes.
Summary: While at Lake Michigan, saw several lights in airplane-like formation. Made no sound and moved slowly.
